Before I upgrade, please can you describe what has changed and/or add a tag referring to the release?
title: What's changed in 0.3.3?

text: ok, just seen the tag. still changes.txt update would be good

There's a new version of [pytest-xdist](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pytest-xdist) available. You are currently using **1.18.0**. I have updated it to **1.18.1** These links might come in handy: PyPI | Changelog | Repo ### Changelog > >### 1.18.1 >================================ >Bug Fixes >--------- >- Fixed serialization of ``longrepr.sections`` during error reporting from > workers. (`171 <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest-xdist/issues/171>`_) >- Fix ``ReprLocal`` not being unserialized breaking --showlocals usages. (`176 > <https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest-xdist/issues/176>`_) *Got merge conflicts? Close this PR and delete the branch. I'll create a new PR for you.* Happy merging! ðŸ¤–
